    <div ><h1 class="mt-3">Guide to Best’s Credit Ratings</h1><p>A Best's Credit Rating (BCR) is a forward-looking, independent, and objective opinion regarding an insurer's, issuer's, or financial obligation's relative creditworthiness. The opinion represents a comprehensive analysis consisting of a quantitative and
    qualitative evaluation of balance sheet strength, operating performance, and business profile or, where appropriate, the specific nature and details of a security.</p><p>Please read&nbsp;the&nbsp;<a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Guide to Best’s Credit Ratings</a>&nbsp;for an in-depth explanation.&nbsp;A BCR is developed considering relevant aspects
    of AM Best <a href="https://web.ambest.com/ratings-services/rating-methodologies" data-sf-ec-immutable="" data-sf-marked="">Rating Methodologies</a>. AM Best assigns various Credit Rating opinions, which are collectively referred to as "Best's
    Credit Ratings" and include:</p><ul><li><a href="http://www.ambest.com/ratings/guide.pdf" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Guide to Best's Financial Strength Ratings (FSR)</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www.ambest.com/ratings/icrguide.pdf" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Guide to Best's Issuer Credit Ratings (ICR)</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www.ambest.com/ratings/debtguide.pdf" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Guide to Best's Issue Credit Ratings (IR)</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www.ambest.com/ratings/nsrguide.pdf" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Guide to Best's National Scale Ratings (NSR)</a> </li></ul><p>In addition, AM Best provides the following rating-related services and information:</p><ul><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#PCA" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Best's Preliminary Credit Assessment (PCA)</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#RAS" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Best's Rating Assessment Service (RAS)</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#RES" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Best's Rating Evaluation Service (RES)</a>
 </li><li><a href="https://web.ambest.com/ratings-services/financial-size-category-(fsc)" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Best's Financial Size Category (FSC)</a>
 </li></ul><p>For more information regarding what a BCR is, how a BCR is developed, or other information related to the production of opinions please reference AM Best's guide, <a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Guide to Best’s Credit Ratings</a> or select a topic below.</p><h2><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Guide to Best’s Credit Ratings <small>(quick links)</small></a></h2><ul><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#Comments" data-sf-ec-immutable="">General Comments</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#page=6" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Rating Process</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#Sources" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Material Sources of Information</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#Quality" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Quality of Information</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#page=11" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Opinion Type Definitions</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#page=14" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Opinion Characteristics &amp; Identifiers</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#page=15" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Opinion Modifiers</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#page=16" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Opinion Outlooks</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#page=17" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Opinion Affiliation Codes</a>
 </li><li><a href="http://www3.ambest.com/ambv/ratingmethodology/OpenPDF.aspx?rc=238151#page=19" data-sf-ec-immutable="">Best's Credit Rating Scales: Categories &amp; Symbols</a> </li></ul></div>    
